Description:
Simplified variant of vasprintf and asprintf.

Files:
lib/vaprintf.c
lib/aprintf.c

Depends-on:
stdio-h
vaszprintf
malloc-posix
xsize
stdarg-h
errno-h

configure.ac:
gl_STDIO_MODULE_INDICATOR([vaprintf])
m4_ifdef([AM_XGETTEXT_OPTION],
